: Kéoulenta, II-VI.1942; Nion, camp 
<collectorName box="[865,922,464,484]" pageId="140" pageNumber="533">du Yâ</collectorName>
, battage du feuillage en sous-bois, forêt primaire, 
<date box="[173,315,494,514]" pageId="140" pageNumber="533" value="1983-12-21" valueMax="1983-12-22" valueMin="1983-12-21">
